0:I ran after Kozupii, but I had taken too long to do so, and now, I couldn't see her anywhere.\n;I hadn't said anything to her about wanting us to leave together, but she was the only person I had left.\p;
100:Losing her started to make me freak out, and I could feel the anxiety slowly welling up.\p;
200:So, knowing I couldn't take it, I gave up on trying to find Kozupii, and decided to hurry back to my base.\p;
