3000:The sound always found me.\n;The gaze always caught up to me.\p;
3100:Every time I thought I got away from the noise, it always started up once again.\p;
3200:In my head, it was like my enemies were multiplying without end.\p;
3300:Eventually, I ran into a red light, forcing me to stop.\p;
3400:Planting my hands on my knees, I tried as best I could to catch my breath, all while the noise of the shutters persisted.\p;
